CacheStorageKeys.summary:
The keys() method of the interface returns a {{jsxref("Promise")}} that will resolve with an array containing strings corresponding to all of the named objects tracked by the object in the order they were created.
Use this method to iterate over a list of all objects.

remarks.para: You can access CacheStorage through the global property.

CacheStorageKeys.returns: a {{jsxref("Promise")}} that resolves with an array of the names inside the object.
